{"tid":1776470,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國女團「軍隊人氣」票選前11名，兵哥哥最喜歡的竟是她？？","createTime":"2019-12-09T14:23:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T05:30:32.000Z","uid":33359,"like":28,"dislike":281,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"2f6b8365ef9810cfa0bb0a78a37e8df41ba7aa5d","tid":1776470,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T14:23:05.000Z","msg":"TOP 11： TWICE MOMO<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/vu7hr9pclec11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2Fvu7hr9pclec11.jpg&h=55884fed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今年23歲的MOMO出生於日本京都市，並於2015年隨組合TWICE出道，憑藉著紮實的舞蹈功底和高超的歌唱實力而備受粉絲喜愛。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTOP 10：IZ*ONE 張元英<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3682/d3682045.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3682%2Fd3682045.jpg&h=3eb09857&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年通過選秀節目《PRODUCE 48》「C位」出道，因為有著優越的身材比例，再加上清純美貌，一度被冠上了「天生偶像」的稱號。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTOP 9：TWICE 林娜璉<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.5669.com/uploads/allimg/160316/62-16031616004L00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.5669.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F160316%2F62-16031616004L00.jpg&h=e2200e64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n娜璉雖然是隊里年紀最大的，但卻有一股清新、可愛的少女魅力，笑起來露出標誌性的「兔牙」更是相當討喜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTOP 8：BLACKPINK Jennie<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/7c/4b/4b/7c4b4bcc37e6d5dda4ec646f5acaae9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F7c%2F4b%2F4b%2F7c4b4bcc37e6d5dda4ec646f5acaae9c.jpg&h=5f2ba559&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有著「人間香奈兒」外號的Jennie，出道前就已經累積了相當豐富的活動經驗，出道後更是憑藉著美貌和實力虜獲了大批粉絲芳心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTOP 7：BLACKPINK Jisoo<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/38/81/49/388149f131d24f792003ee01229dc0fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F38%2F81%2F49%2F388149f131d24f792003ee01229dc0fb.jpg&h=ce68c53e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n出眾的外貌經常讓人眼前一亮，而在唱歌、舞蹈、表演等方面的實力也不容小覷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTOP 6：Red Velvet Joy<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.asianjunkie.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/JoyRedVelvet-600x377.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.asianjunkie.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2FJoyRedVelvet-600x377.jpg&h=0ed30de2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJoy有著一張可愛的娃娃臉，看起來就像鄰家小妹妹一般，笑容很甜，眼睛也總是水亮又無辜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTOP 5：Red Velvet 姜澀琪<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.people.com.cn/mediafile/pic/20140801/25/13946766831390252533.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.people.com.cn%2Fmediafile%2Fpic%2F20140801%2F25%2F13946766831390252533.jpg&h=a3f8f082&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n打破傳統的SM審美，澀琪作為社內唯一的單眼皮女藝人，憑藉著獨特的魅力受到了很多粉絲的喜愛。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTOP 4：Red Velvet Irene<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.teepr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/irene-bae-joo-hyun-red-velvet-2019-billboard-1548.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teepr.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2Firene-bae-joo-hyun-red-velvet-2019-billboard-1548.jpg&h=f7b091b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIrene的顏值應該是公認的吧？還曾被評選為第四代女團中的第一神顏，舞台上也一直展現著不一樣的魅力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTOP 3：TWICE 子瑜<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/OH8QWj5IGCI/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FOH8QWj5IGCI%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=77ef5a93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n子瑜有著一雙像小鹿般清澈的大眼睛，也是TWICE中唯一一個來自台灣的成員。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTOP 2：TWICE Sana<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://dbkpop.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/twice_fancy_you_concept_sana_profile.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdbkpop.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2Ftwice_fancy_you_concept_sana_profile.jpg&h=b661d5d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSana的高人氣不單單是因為顏值，強大的業務能力也是她圈粉的重要原因。<br />\n<br />\nTOP 1：TWICE 定延<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/BowedWaterloggedFennecfox-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FBowedWaterloggedFennecfox-size_restricted.gif&h=0710fb0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/AbleOldDalmatian-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FAbleOldDalmatian-size_restricted.gif&h=8159e57f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n定延的短髮造型帥氣可愛，長髮造型美麗動人，外表是TWICE中的顏值擔當，更是香港連登論壇公認的南韓第一美女，拿第一名也是理所當然吧？"},{"pid":"0e6db7944a60bccba221b86505c21ee4611c0c94","tid":1776470,"uid":18581,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T14:24:40.000Z","msg":"假的"},{"pid":"d73731111f84d61bd0dd3fbc2e8b0cccbdb095e1","tid":1776470,"uid":92680,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T14:24:46.000Z","msg":"軍人多gay佬是常識吧"},{"pid":"451f127ad19e86fe34e1cc6eb08603a79e2e8cfb","tid":1776470,"uid":74065,"like":90,"dislike":0,"score":90,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T14:25:04.000Z","msg":"REPORT假新聞可以封AC <br />\n邊狗試過"},{"pid":"faa30df65a91c553e2cac26c7062a2b10bc0604a","tid":1776470,"uid":149371,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T14:25:04.000Z","msg":"資料來源：印佬"},{"pid":"404de4d225e873d423b89d563c0c0af3e94a4166","tid":1776470,"uid":305631,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T14:25:28.000Z","msg":"第一名仔嚟嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"badc4a817856a9472efaba104e616025352fd4ce","tid":1776470,"uid":305631,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"404de4d225e873d423b89d563c0c0af3e94a4166","tid":1776470,"uid":305631,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T14:25:28.000Z","msg":"第一名仔嚟嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T14:26:04.000Z","msg":"非"},{"pid":"0003730ae9b35e0b9effd7f07d96786516024b5d","tid":1776470,"uid":76632,"like":5,"d